room_title: Escape room "Grimm Cabin" by Escape Room Entertainment in Melbourne
room_address: 604 E New Haven Ave, Melbourne, FL 32901
room_description:
Once upon a time, there was a cabin deep in the woods of fairytale land. The cabin was home to two brothers who are responsible for many magical stories. It was known as Grimm cabin. Rumors are it is now protected by an evil witch.
Despite the rumors, many have searched far and wide to find the cabin to find the treasures and potions within. The most highly sought is the potion of life which has many great powers. After traveling through the woods, you have stumbled upon Grimm cabin. You notice you only have 30 minutes before the wicked witch returns to the cabin.
